00:08:20.770 --> 00:08:22.070
&gt;&gt; J.D. Vance: Yeah, that's right.

00:08:22.070 --> 00:08:23.370
I think so.

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:24.810
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:So,
now what has been the reaction

00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:26.110
