00:09:33.830 --> 00:09:35.130
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:Okay.

00:09:35.130 --> 00:09:37.420 position:56%
So let's talk about the book itself.

00:09:37.420 --> 00:09:41.030
I have read it, and I
