00:10:12.470 --> 00:10:13.770
&gt;&gt; J.D. Vance: Sure.

00:10:13.770 --> 00:10:15.070
&gt;&gt; David M. Rubenstein:All right.

00:10:15.070 --> 00:10:16.370
First, the writing style.

00:10:16.370 --> 00:10:17.910
Were you a gifted writer
